The 7 Line Army
description:
// Fans ask all the time "how can I join your Army?". There's a simple answer. If you know about us, you're already in. You don't need to sit with us at a game to be in the same boat. We all have the same mindset. We're die hard fans who love this team in the good times and bad. We come together to form a community of like minded fans. It doesn't matter if you cheer with us from the ball park or thousands of miles away on your couch. When you're in our "Army" you'll always have someone to relate to. We're all in this together and the victories in future Octobers are going to be that much sweeter. If you get a chance we do plan outings around once a month. Pick up a ticket and make some new friends. Everyone is welcome. UNITED WE CHEER!

// The official t-shirt of "The 7 Line Army". S-4XL mens and S-2XL women's versions available. Super soft vintage feeling t-shirts.

Loyal 'Til The Last Out
description:
SOLD OUT IN UNDER 3 HOURS!! SEE YOU ALL AT CITI! 

This will be our 7th outing of 2013. Let's go out with a bang! We are 3-3 in events this year. Lets finish our season above .500!

IMPORTANT: If you'd like to sit with friends, you MUST order the tickets in the same transaction.

The package is $58 each and includes:

- Ticket in the Big Apple Reserve. (field level next to the HR Apple)

- Special event t-shirt. (seen above and NOT sold separately)

- Mike Piazza t-shirt giveaway from Citi Field as you walk in.

- Mike Piazza pre-game Mets HOF induction ceremony. 

- One HECK of a great time with 100's of other die hard fans. Yes, we'll have our signature thunder sticks and other fun giveaways during the game.

- After party in McFadden's. (21+) FREE KEGS, NO COVER. All you need to do is wear your "Loyal 'Til The Last Out" event t-shirt after the game.

WOMENS: S - 2XL t-shirt available
MENS: S-4XL t-shirt available

PICK YOUR APPROPRIATE SIZE FROM THE DROP DOWN MENU BELOW AND DOUBLE CHECK IT BEFORE CHECKING OUT. THANKS!
